{
  "3077060": {
    "name": "三国群英传：格斗版",
    "steam_appid": 3077060,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >系列最新格斗游戏《三国群英传：格斗版》震撼登场，开启全新格斗时代！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打破系列一贯的策略框架，《三国群英传》这回把战场搬上了格斗擂台！您熟悉的关羽、吕布、赵云等三国名将，将以兵器招式、连段博弈在战场上一决高下。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■三国名将兵器对决</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三国名将全员登场！夏侯惇、荀彧、关羽、吕布、孙尚香、貂蝉等熟悉角色，各自拿起专属兵器展开激烈对决。大斧、长剑、长刀、长戟、长枪——每一种武器都能打出截然不同的格斗节奏。以爽快的连段系统与高还原的战斗演出，带你体验最热血的三国格斗战场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077060/extras/a3f62dcca2bd0ac60fe5b5e6d81679f0.poster.avif?t=1765430268\" width=1170 height=572 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077060/extras/a3f62dcca2bd0ac60fe5b5e6d81679f0.webm?t=1765430268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077060/extras/a3f62dcca2bd0ac60fe5b5e6d81679f0.mp4?t=1765430268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■简单连段，畅快格斗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色连段设计直觉好上手，不需繁複输入即可连接多段攻击。不同招式间能自由派生出多样组合，冷兵器对战也能打出华丽又具冲击感的连段。整体表现写实不浮夸，让每一次命中都充满紧张感与热血的临场刺激。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077060/extras/be2dc08560d1b22ccca2047bad3b0399.poster.avif?t=1765430268\" width=1170 height=636 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077060/extras/be2dc08560d1b22ccca2047bad3b0399.webm?t=1765430268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077060/extras/be2dc08560d1b22ccca2047bad3b0399.mp4?t=1765430268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■3D格斗，轻松上手的极限对战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作採用横向对打的3D格斗系统，加入可自由侧移的立体走位机制，让攻防节奏更具深度。招式输入简单、节奏明快，没有複杂的转招操作；无论新手或老玩家，都能迅速上手享受格斗乐趣。透过取消、浮空与追击组成连段，结合立回与场景互动，带来爽快又可深挖的战斗体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077060/extras/cf1566b0292fd4845e0d2f2561331491.poster.avif?t=1765430268\" width=1170 height=546 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077060/extras/cf1566b0292fd4845e0d2f2561331491.webm?t=1765430268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077060/extras/cf1566b0292fd4845e0d2f2561331491.mp4?t=1765430268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■双武装切换，展现多变战斗风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位武将皆能同时装备主、副两种武器，战斗中可自由切换，带来节奏转换与策略变化。不同武器拥有各自的攻击范围与动作节奏，让一场对决中能体验两种截然不同的战斗手感，打造属于自己的连段风格与战斗节奏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077060/extras/ba30dde1b64104dda69d215745989341.poster.avif?t=1765430268\" width=1170 height=544 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077060/extras/ba30dde1b64104dda69d215745989341.webm?t=1765430268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077060/extras/ba30dde1b64104dda69d215745989341.mp4?t=1765430268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■爆发极限的大招反击</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当进入黄血阶段时，角色可施展威力惊人的超必杀技，瞬间扭转战局。无需複杂操作，只要简单指令即可释放华丽招式与震撼特效，在强烈的打击感中完成逆转，带来最纯粹、最刺激的格斗体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077060/extras/7472f76a4088fe02d309e25479f81370.poster.avif?t=1765430268\" width=1170 height=544 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077060/extras/7472f76a4088fe02d309e25479f81370.webm?t=1765430268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077060/extras/7472f76a4088fe02d309e25479f81370.mp4?t=1765430268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
